A 40 year old man slipped and drowned in River Gicagai in Kibugu village Embu North sub-county on bridge which is under construction.Nelson Murithi, drowned in River Gicagai on Thursday in Kibugu village, Embu North subcounty. It is believed he was walking on a bridge under construction when he slipped and fell. Embu North police boss Mark Wanjala said rains have made the bridge slippery.